		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Weapon (Any Melee Weapon) - Legendary (Requires Attunement)</p><p><em>This finely balanced blade lets you trade accuracy for a magical guard.</em></p><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with the weapon.</p></li><li><p>The first time you attack with it on each of your turns, you may transfer any amount of the weapon's bonus to your &amp;Reference[Armor Class] until the start of your next turn (for example, attack and damage +1, AC +2).</p></li><li><p>You must be holding the weapon to benefit from the bonus to AC.</p></li></ul><p>@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.content24.JournalEntry.dmgFoundryRefere.JournalEntryPage.Ok4iCgD25ENgoRxE cite=false caption=false classes=\"hide-in-embed\"]</p>",
